I’m 29 today!! 🎂💝✨ 2023 was not an easy year but it brought so many beautiful things into my life. I feel a newfound sense of clarity, motivation and empowerment as 2024 starts and I enter my next chapter. I’m grateful to be surrounded by the most incredible, supportive people (including all of you)-thank you for making me feel so loved and for allowing me to share my life with you. 🤍
